hackathon-description-text: HypeHacks is student run 48-hour hackathon created to hype up the hackathons we know and love, as well as to honor Tristan Wiley’s birthday. It is scheduled to begin on
hackathon-eligibility: Anyone can enter! Any age! Anyone!
hackathon-requirements: As long as you make it during the allotted time, you're free to build whatever.

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: You get a hug next time you see Tristan! MHacks? ;)

hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: All enteries will be judged by Sir Hype (birthday boy) and his chosen ones. They will choose based on originality, creativity, and HYPENESS!

hackathon-description-header: Birthday hackathon for the Hype King Tristan Wiley!
